<br />&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;!--[endif]--&gt;The solar energy charger can be quickly recharged. Three minutes altogether will be enough to recharge the complete &quot;dead cell phone&quot;. What's more, the cell phone can be recharged the same time when you are having the battery being recharged.&lt;/p&gt;
<br />&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Also, you can use the solar energy charge to recharge your cell phone directly with the power from the electric outlets.&lt;/p&gt;
<br />&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;Attention:&lt;/p&gt;
<br />&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Avoid soaking it into the water and strong collision.&lt;/p&gt;
<br />&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Keep the surface of the battery board smooth and clean. Avoid scratches to it.&lt;/p&gt;
<br />&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;3.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Turn it to &quot;on&quot; status when you are charging your cell phone, and &quot;off&quot; when you have the charging done.&lt;/p&gt;
<br />&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;4.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;!--[endif]--&gt;The LED light will be on when you have it exposed to sunlight which means the battery is being recharged. Therefore, turn the switch to the &quot;off&quot; status then.&lt;/p&gt;
